Linear fit attempt:
  Eq2-Eq1: 3a - 6b = -18 => a - 2b = -6
  Eq3-Eq2: 4a - 8b = 4 => a - 2b = 1
  CONTRADICTION: H is NOT linear in (ov0, ov1)

Quadratic fit: H = 1*ov0^2 + (-23)*ov0 + 301
  ov0=14: H_pred=175, H_actual=175, match=YES
  ov0=14: H_pred=175, H_actual=175, match=YES
  ov0=10: H_pred=171, H_actual=171, match=YES
  ov0=10: H_pred=171, H_actual=171, match=YES
  ov0=14: H_pred=175, H_actual=175, match=YES
